Package: mdpr
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the minimal policy for a finite-horizon Markov decision process
Version: 1.0.0
Author: person("Carson", "James", email = "carson.a.james@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Carson James <carson.a.james@gmail.com>
Description: Uses a dynamic programming algorithm known as "value iteration" to 
    choose an optimal policy for a finite horizon Markov decision process with 
    finitely many states and actions.
